OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1782323307
OL,3,CStorms cause floods and big travel
OL,4,Cdisruption across London
OL,6,FLondon Fire Brigade said it had taken
OL,7,Faround 400 calls since midnight after
OL,8,Fa series of intense thunderstorms
OL,9,Fstruck the capital.
OL,11,FFirefighters were called to flooding
OL,12,Faffecting a number of properties along
OL,13,Fwith at least two house fires possibly
OL,14,Ftriggered by lightning strikes.
OL,16,FSome areas were also hit by flash
OL,17,Fflooding including roads. Drivers were
OL,18,Fbeing urged not to drive through
OL,19,Ffloodwater and take extra care.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/5
